node.text:
Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer is unlike any other hard seltzer out there. Born out of innovation, we knew we needed branding and cans that matched the unique and delicious liquid inside. Our Senior Graphic Designer Cara, and local folk artist, Alynn are here to guide you through the inspiration and all the details that go into the Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer branding! Then bring Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer home to admire for yourself by heading to our beer finder at the link in our bio.
 #foundersbrewing #reachforreal #alcanzarloreal

Our education team is saddened they can’t host all of you for their famous brewery tours. So, we decided to do the next best thing and start a weekly beer education video series. Starting today, we’ll be releasing weekly beer education videos to help you pass the time and hopefully, help you come out of this with some new beer knowledge.

In today’s video, John and Marklyn are talking about the importance of proper glassware. Grab a beer, pour it into your favorite mug, tumbler or snifter and let the beer education begin. If you enjoy this video feel free to let us know what other topics you would like them to cover in future videos. #chaseyourwhatif

A clean brewery is a happy brewery! ⁠
⁠
Sure hops, malts and yeast are the stars of the beer but they wouldn’t shine as bright as they do without a clean brewery. That’s why we clean everything - and we mean everything - to the highest standard to ensure each beer tastes exactly as it should every time. #foundersbrewing

node.text:
It's Sunday - or should we say Sundae - and you know what that means? It's time for beer floats! Everyone loves ice cream, adding an ice-cold can of Cerise is just the cherry on top. ⁠
⁠
What's your favorite beer and ice cream combo?⁠
#foundersbrewing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, drink and outdoors.

node.text:
Any occasion can be a vacation - if you play your cards right. Where are you taking All Day Vacay this weekend?⁠
⁠
📸:@joshwebb88 on IG⁠
#foundersbrewing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 16, 2021. May be an image of bottle and indoor.

node.text:
Saddle up. Highball Drifter is now available in our taprooms!⁠
⁠
This second entry in our Bottle Shop Series is a cocktail-inspired, bourbon barrel-aged ale that’s sure to knock your chaps off. Its aromatics of caramel and vanilla mingle with subtle hints of cherry and bitter orange peel to create a bold flavor with a moderate sweetness and a warming finish. ⁠
⁠
You can try Highball Drifter on draft and in 4-packs of bottles in our taprooms and Company Store now! Those not in the area can expect to see it on shelves nationally in the coming weeks. #foundersbrewing⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 15, 2021. May be an image of drink and food.

node.text:
Beer and Hard Seltzer share more similarities than you might expect!⁠
⁠
We know a lot of you are beer fans first and foremost but this brief rundown might shed some light on why so many breweries, us included, are in the hard seltzer game. Head to the link in our bio to learn more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 14, 2021. May be an image of bottle.

node.text:
You’re going to want to put on your robe and cue your favorite jazz album for this one. Introducing: Velvet Rush.⁠
⁠
Inspired by high-end craft cocktails and moody jazz clubs, Velvet Rush takes the bourbon barrel-aged brown ale up an octave with free-flowing notes of coffee, chocolate and vanilla. Milk sugar weaves together this complex tapestry of flavors to create a unique sipping experience that really ties the room together and comes in at 11.1% ABV.⁠
⁠
Velvet Rush will be available on draft and in 4-packs of bottles in our taprooms on August 6. The rest of you can expect to see it nationwide in September. Head to the link in our bio for details! #foundersbrewing⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 13, 2021. May be an image of bottle and indoor.

node.text:
Beer fridge: summertime edition.⁠
⁠
This sweet and tangy masterpiece made with fresh raspberries is the ultimate summer sipper. Don’t forget to stock up so you too can sit back and enjoy the season the right way.⁠
⁠
What's in your beer fridge right now? #foundersbrewing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 12, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
It's what's on the inside of the can that counts.⁠
⁠
Can you guess what beer this is? #foundersbrewing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Founders Brewing Co. on July 12, 2021 tagging @summercampfest. May be an image of text.

node.text:
We’re the official craft beer sponsor of this year’s Summer Camp Music Festival, and to celebrate, we’re partnering with our friends @summercampfest to give away the ultimate VIP Experience!⁠
⁠
You could win two 3-Day General Admission passes with VIP upgrades and see acts like Billy Strings, Rezz, GRiZ and more. We’re topping off these passes with a side stage viewing experience, cooler, hammock, air lounger and other merch that’s essential for any festival adventure.⁠
⁠
All you have to do is:⁠
⁠
- Share a photo to your social media with the hashtag #founderscamp21 of you enjoying outdoors (bonus points if you’re enjoying some live music or have one of our beers with you)!⁠
⁠
OR⁠
⁠
- Submit a short essay detailing your love for live music and what winning the contest would mean to you.⁠
⁠
You have until 5pm on July 28 to enter. Head to the link in our bio for contest rules and details. Good luck! #foundersbrewing #founderscamp21

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Founders Brewing Co. on July 11, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
Lazy Sunday with Centennial IPA? Count us in.⁠
⁠
It’s been quite the weekend, friends. We hope you’re taking time to relax and enjoy a beer today. You deserve it. #foundersbrewing

node.text:
Beer or Hard Seltzer?⁠
⁠
Whether you’re headed to the beach with a Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer or All Day Vacay, choosing the right drink to bring along with you is an important decision. Good thing we’ve got something perfect for every occasion. #foundersbrewing
